OL,6,FIn the once-vibrant suburb of
OL,7,FAltadena, the wounds are still raw.
OL,8,FNat and Shant walk through the charred
OL,9,Fskeleton of their former home,
OL,10,Fpointing out what remains: a rusting
OL,11,Fbike frame, the warped remains of a
OL,12,Fdining table, the blackened metal of
OL,13,Ftheir old bed frames.
OL,15,F"Everything's rusting now," said
OL,16,FShant. "That tells you how much time
OL,17,Fhas passed."
OL,19,FNat and Shant face an uphill battle to
OL,20,Frebuild after losing their childhood
OL,21,Fhome
