OL,6,FThis wasn't just another California
OL,7,Fwildfire. It was a perfect storm,
OL,8,Fdriven by a changing climate. Eight
OL,9,Fmonths with no measurable rainfall.
OL,10,FRecord-breaking heat. And the
OL,11,Fnotorious Santa Ana winds ` blowing at
OL,12,Fup to 100 miles an hour.
