OL,3,CAfter the inferno: Can Los Angeles
OL,4,Crise from the ashes?
OL,6,F"Climate change is at the heart of
OL,7,Fthese fires. It's an accelerant. You
OL,8,Fmight as well have added fuel to these
OL,9,Fflames ` but it was also driven by
OL,10,Fwind," said environmental analyst
OL,11,FProfessor Char Miller. "If you have
OL,12,Fwind speeds of 90 to a hundred miles
OL,13,Fan hour, there is nothing you can
OL,14,Fdo..."
OL,16,FThe fires destroyed more than 16,000
OL,17,Fbuildings and displaced more than
OL,18,F200,000 people. In Altadena alone,
OL,19,Fnearly 9,000 structures were lost.
