OL,6,FAfter initially sleeping in an empty
OL,7,Foffice block, Brenda Lopez and her
OL,8,Fdaughter Mileydis had no option but to
OL,9,Freturn to their apartment. For three
OL,10,Fmonths, they lived without gas,
OL,11,Felectricity, or hot water `
OL,12,Feffectively camping in a smoke-damaged
OL,13,Fbuilding.
OL,15,FThey're still living just steps away
OL,16,Ffrom a neighbourhood reduced to ash.
OL,17,FThe health risks are real, but like
OL,18,Fmany others caught in LA's housing
OL,19,Fcrisis, they simply have nowhere else
OL,20,Fto go.
